ttsdata.text: Hello there. My name is Cody Anderson, the younger brother of Kye You Anderson. You may be wondering why you got this 4 0 4 error.
Well, unfortunately, a serious error has occured when the video was loading. The video you were wanting to watch could not be found at this time.
You should try refreshing the page to see if the video loads properly. If that doesn't work, please wait several minutes, and then come back and try again.
Um, Cody, what are you doing?
Oh, I'm just telling the viewers that the video they were trying to watch could not be found at this time. They will need to try again later.
Cody, what are you talking about? This isn't actually a 4 0 4 error. This is just a drawing on the wall that you made right next to Daisy and Lily's room.
What? No. This really is a 4 0 4 error. I promise that the viewer was looking for a video but it got redirected to here instead.
I'm just gonna zoom the camera out to prove it.
See? Just a drawing. What do you have to say for yourself?
Okay look. I just wanted to roleplay one of those 4 0 4 errors you see when some website messes up when trying to load. I wanted to see what people would think.
I mean, it's not like people would fall for this anyway. Now if you'll excuse me, I'm just gonna stop this recording.
Are you really this dumb? I can see that camera recording what you are doing. I bet it's zoomed in just to only show the drawing you're standing in front of.
If that doesn't work, you will need to wait a while before trying again.
